DML or drawing markup language created by viraj sharma is a markup language to draw things with staright lines.The tag details are given below:

1 - forward tag
forward tag makes line go front and it asks for unit to makes line move front in units
2 - backward tag
backward tag makes line go back and it asks for unit to makes line move front in units
3 - left tag
left tag makes line go left and it asks for degree for line angle
4 - right tag
right tag makes line go right and it asks for degree for line angle

syntaxes are given below:

1 - forward tag - <forward>units</forward>
2 - backward tag - <backward>units</backward>
3 - left tag - <left>degree</left>
4 - right tag - <right>degree</right>


